{
  "stem": "323.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She might suggest you should take-- do this or that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she never said go to church with us, celebrate Christmas with us, ever, at any time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, in Stockholm, she made it her business to find a Jewish organization for me, yes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had only Swedish friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, my friend Hilda, from Theresienstadt, was in Stockholm for a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through this Jewish organization I went to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did spend some time together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was great to find her, great that she was alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you're such different people, even now, I mean-- we have-- we have some of our past in common, but that's about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we are completely different people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And she is the typical kind of woman who would be very happy to settle down, get married and have children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that would be her life, which is not enough for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was just-- I didn't see that much of her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Basically, my contact was with Swedish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my friends were Swedes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did you find Dita?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Red Cross finally came across, and Dita was able to contact me in Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was living in London at the time, going to nursing school, where she became a nurse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she never did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, she did come to Canada, but that's later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to school in Sweden, and I loved every-- every moment I spent in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I realize what this woman has done for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't think there are very many people on this earth that will do what she did, without-- no personal gain whatsoever, just because she wanted to be a kind human being.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she put you through the university?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
